data.description: Introducing a charming .3-acre property nestled in the heart of Florence, Colorado, where the serenity of the countryside meets breathtaking mountain views. This unique parcel features a cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home, making it an ideal haven for those seeking a tranquil and comfortable lifestyle. The property's generous .3-acre lot provides ample space for outdoor enjoyment and expansion possibilities, all while offering a sense of privacy and tranquility. Enjoy the picturesque scenery of Colorado's majestic mountains right from your own doorstep, creating a stunning backdrop for everyday living. Inside, the well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home offers a comfortable and functional living space, perfect for families or individuals looking to settle in a peaceful environment. The home's design maximizes the scenic views, allowing you to appreciate the natural beauty that surrounds you.
